
	INSTALLATION TIPS FOR VIPLIB
====================================


 Connect to VIPLib SVN repository and checkout,
 you will be sure to have last version of VIPLib.
    [ svn://mmlab.science.unitn.it/VIPLib ]


 Please read ./COMPILE for more informations, or have a look to VIPLib website 


Windows
=======

  Since it would take long, we decided to remove the binaries from the website. All users
  are requested to download the library from the repository and compile the MSVC workspace/solution



Linux
=====

  Required components may be installed easily on new distributions:

	o  apt-get install build-essential
	
	o  apt-get install libqt4-gui *
	   apt-get install libqt4-dev *


  * There are some problems on new releases, we are working to fix them.
